tga '''Tadrart''' yat tgrawt illan ɣ izzlmḍ n [[Agadir|ugadir]]. twala i tanbaḍt n imuzzar idawtanan, lli iḍfarn i tamnbaḍt n (u) [[Tamnbaḍt n Agadir-Idawtanan|Agadir-Idawtanan]].

ar gis ittwayskar yan ugadaz anmalass (ssuqq) kra ygat ass n usiḍyas (ssabt), d ar gis ittwayskar yan unmuggar lmusm n tdrart, ɣ tizi n unbdu (ṣṣiɣ) ɣ tigira n wayyur n ɣuct.

